  "name": "2 Corinthians 5:1–10",
  "localizedName": "2 Corinthians 5:1–10",
  "content": [
    {
      "tiptap": {
        "type": "doc",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Paul described human bodies like tents that will not last for ever. Believers will have new bodies after they are raised from the dead."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Paul described the new bodies like a building or a house that will last for ever. These bodies will be full of Jesus’ powerful life and can never be destroyed."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Believers long for their new bodies. They long to be with their "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "resourceReference",
                    "attrs": {
                      "resourceId": "108329",
                      "resourceType": "BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "text": "Lord"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "The Holy Spirit lives in believers now. The Spirit is a sign and a promise that they will be with the Lord. That will happen when "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "resourceReference",
                    "attrs": {
                      "resourceId": "108055",
                      "resourceType": "BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "text": "judgement day"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " comes."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
